section.jumbotron.d-flex.flex-row.justify-content-end
  h1.mr-5.text-info 
    | Registration 
section.container 
  form.column(method='post' action='/signup')
    .form-group.col-md-5 
      h3 
        span.col-auto.badge.badge-warning
        | Registration 
    .form-group.col-md-5 
      label(for='email')
        | Email address 
        span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
          | *
      input.form-control(type='email' name='email' aria-describedby='emailHelp' placeholder='Enter email' required='') 
      small#emailHelp.form-text.text-muted
      | We&apos;ll never share your email with anyone else. 
    .form-group.col-md-5
      label(for='inputPassword1') 
        | Password 
        span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
          | * 
      input.form-control(type='password' name='password_1' placeholder='Password' required='') 
    .form-group.col-md-5
      label(for='inputPassword2') 
        | Confirm password 
        span(style='color: red; display: inline; float: none;') 
          | * 
      input.form-control(type='password' name='password_2' placeholder='Password' required='') 
    .form-group.col-md-5
      button.btn.btn-outline-warning(type='submit' name='reg_volunteer') 
        | I&apos;m a buddy
      button.btn.btn-outline-warning(type='submit' name='reg_seeker') 
        | I&apos;m a buddy seeker 
    .form-group.col-md-5 
    p.col-md-5 
      | Already a member?
      a.text-warning(href='/login') 
        | Log in